  • Enum Constant Details

    • INTAKE

      public static final IDataIntegrityService.LifecycleStep INTAKE
      Triggered as data enters the submission process, before any data is sent to external services. This allows for the "first word" about data coming into the system.

    • PRE_STORE

      public static final IDataIntegrityService.LifecycleStep PRE_STORE
      Triggered immediately before data is stored to the database, but after Leap normal submission processing, including the consumption of data coming back from external services. This step allows for the "last word" before data is stored in the database.
